item.title: CVE-2023-27921|2024-08-02T12:23:30.807Z -- jins%20inc. -- jins%20meme%20core
item.description: JINS MEME CORE Firmware version 2.2.0 and earlier uses a hard-coded cryptographic key, which may lead to data acquired by a sensor of the affected product being decrypted by a network-adjacent attacker.
